# AXIOM validator seed list — bootstrap entries for fresh wallet
# installs. Community-maintained: PR against axiom-dist to add /
# retire entries. Wallets fetch this on first launch and discover
# the rest of the network via gossip.
#
# Format (quoted CSV, 3 fields):
#   "name", "ed25519 pubkey (64 hex, or empty)", "carriers"
# carriers: comma-separated <scheme>:<addr> (email, TOT, FATMAMA, P2P).
# An empty pubkey => the wallet ships a Plain (unsealed) UMP; a present
# key => the UMP body is sealed to it (Ed25519 -> X25519).
